Ecuador 1957


Qualified for the final round: the winners and runners-up of the
Campeonato Profesional Interandinos (Quito and Ambato) and of the
Campeonato Profesional de Fútbol de Guayaquil.

Interandinos: champions:  Deportivo Quito
              runners-up: Aucas
Guayaquil:    champions:  Emelec
              runners-up: Barcelona

Campeonato de Fútbol de Guayaquil:

First Stage:

 1.Emelec              12  10  2  0  33-11  22   [Guayaquil]
 2.Barcelona           12   9  2  1  29-16  20   [Guayaquil]
 3.Valdez              12   6  3  3  21-15  15   [Guayaquil]
 4.Everest             12   4  3  5  23-23  11   [Guayaquil]
 5.Patria              12   3  2  7  18-25   8   [Guayaquil]
 6.Nueve de Octubre    12   2  2  8  11-25   6   [Guayaquil]
 7.Español             12   1  0 11  11-31   2   [Guayaquil]

Final Round (includes first stage):

 1.Emelec              15  11  3  1  39-16  25
 2.Barcelona           15  11  2  2  36-21  24
 3.Valdez              15   6  5  4  24-19  17
 4.Everest             15   5  4  6  30-32  14

